A political message is unavoidable
In this form, 139 recordings of British air force soldiers have already been accessed on the Internet, and more than 75,000 people have already looked at their "channel".
The British Department of Defense registered in the spring of 2007 as "defenseheadquarters" and publishes recordings of events in Iraq and Afghanistan, while the British Department of State (Commonwealth Office) and the International Peacekeeping Force in Iraq (MNFI) have their own YouTube channels.
Deployment in Afghanistan
