He's headed for a huge strike.
The League of Trade Unions, or the National Union of Workers' Councils (MOSZ), will set up its strike committee on Friday to coordinate Monday's indefinite strike.
A protest public assembly will be held on Saturday, and work will be halted on Monday - the day of the final vote on the health insurance law.
